|  | spin | double | 0.000 \le \text{spin} \le 5.000 | Quantifies the localized rotational momentum vector over active nodes. |
|  | temp (T) | double | 0.000 \le T \le 1.000 | Thermal tensor metric. Lower temperatures match optimal equilibrium states. |
| **Physics Arc** | throat_radius | double | 15.000 \le R_{\text{throat}} \le 60.000 | Main geometric contraction parameter of the 6-Cylinder boundary layer. |
|  | belt_radius | double | 50.000 \le R_{\text{belt}} \le 100.000 | Redundant confinement parameter tracking structural response fields. |
